<AUTHOR>maxell106</AUTHOR>
<TEXT>The most beautiful car I have ever owned, I was debating between this Mercedes and a BMW 325 but this car just looks 10 times better. The only complaint I have is that it does not have bluetooth, mp3, and ipod kit standard, even the Scion tc which is a $ 18k car has the ipod kit and it reads mp3 standard. But other than that it's the best car for the money. Can't wait to get out of work for the drive home. </TEXT>
<FAVORITE>Interior & exterior design, E85 fuel, blue tints, rear shade, very comfortable.</FAVORITE>
